# VectorShift Frontend Assessment — Implementation Plan

## Goal
Build a production-quality, scalable pipeline builder that scores in the **top 10%** of submissions — with clean architecture, polished UI, robust backend logic, and smart UX. Every design decision is intentional and defensible.

