## Part 3 — 5 New Node Types (all use BaseNode)

| Node | Inputs | Outputs | Fields |
|------|--------|---------|--------|
| **Filter** | `data` | `pass`, `fail` | condition dropdown (contains / equals / not empty) |
| **API Call** | `url`, `body` | `response`, `error` | method dropdown (GET/POST/PUT), headers textarea |
| **Note** | — | — | large textarea for comments (no handles) |
| **Transform** | `input` | `output` | code textarea with JS expression |
| **Math** | `a`, `b` | `result` | operation dropdown (+, -, ×, ÷, mod) |

Each is ~20-30 lines, reusing BaseNode. Clean, consistent, scalable.

