## UI Design System

### Color coding by node type
| Type | Accent Color |
|------|-------------|
| Input | `#6366f1` (indigo) |
| Output | `#10b981` (emerald) |
| LLM | `#f59e0b` (amber) |
| Text | `#3b82f6` (blue) |
| Filter | `#ef4444` (red) |
