| Note | `#6b7280` (gray) |
| Transform | `#06b6d4` (cyan) |
| Math | `#ec4899` (pink) |

### BaseNode visual style
- Rounded corners (`border-radius: 12px`)
- Colored top header bar per type
- Drop shadow + subtle glassmorphism
- Smooth hover effect
- Clean typography (Inter font)

